Package: HapaxLegomena
Type: Package
Title: Analyze Text and Word Distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c( person("T. Tyler Thibeau", email = "thomas.thibeau@maine.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre") )  )
Description: This package reads lines of text and creates a word distribution.
              Analyze word choice trends visually by seeing distribution graphs.
              Look at which words appear 5 or less times. Are there better words
              that could be used in their stead?
